folder: Schenectady Avenue & St. Marks Avenue, Brooklyn, NY
original_title: Brooklyn: Schenectady Avenue - St. Marks Avenue
text:
142 and 140 Schenectady Avenue (right), at the N. W. corner of St. Marks Avenue, showing two old frame dwellings. The small house on the left, with the wooden stairway, is No. 1097 St. Marks Avenue.

September 13, 1940

P.L. Sperr
